PrecisRe-appointment of SUSAN J. FRENCH, of Burnaby, British Columbia, as a full-time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Vancouver Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years, effective June 29, 2001.
